{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I, I'd like to go back to something that happened during when I was fairly young-- I mean, maybe seven, eight years.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it must have happened, like, around 1936, '37.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father owned a reconvalescent home-- sanatorium, in, in the mountain resort that Hitler also later had his-- had his retreat house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was called Obersalzberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's O-B-E-R-S-A-L-Z-B-E-R-G, which means mountain, 'salt mountain berg'-- salt mountain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's near Berchtesgaden, which is a very lovely, scenic resort in the Bavarian Alps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had this-- this was a perfect match for my father because he had the clinic in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after people were recuperating, he would send them, if they could afford it, [LAUGHS] to the sanatorium in the Bavarian Alps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that made perfectly good sense to have this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used that-- we used to go there for vacation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The couple that-- the husband and wife couple that ran this were very loyal people that thought very highly and respected my dad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember being there in the summer of-- it had to be, like, '35, 1935.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I guess I was just eight years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when Hitler had already moved to his house, which was above ours on the mountain--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same area, same, same area, the same mountain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a half an hour walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and word spread that he was, was there in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would greet tourists and shake hands and talk to people and try to be popular.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the governess that we had decided to-- my mother didn't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my-- the governess decided-- and that he is very fond of children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- we went up there-- That's what they-- that Hitler--",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
